'''莉莉·蔻兒'''（'''{{lang|en|Lily Cole}}'''，{{bd|1987年|12月27日|catIdx=C}}），[[英國|英國]][[超級名模|超級名模]]、[[演員|演員]]。

== 早年 ==
莉莉在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[德文郡|德文郡]]的[[托基|托基]]出生，與姊姊Elvie於[[倫敦|倫敦]]長大。

== 模特兒生涯 ==
莉莉在14歲時於[[倫敦蘇豪區|倫敦蘇豪區]]街頭被星探發掘，但她轉身離去<ref name="independent1">{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/profiles/lily-cole-beauty-and-brains-412485.html |title=Lily Cole: Beauty and brains - Profiles, People |publisher=The Independent |date=2006-08-19 |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2009-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220135800/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/profiles/lily-cole-beauty-and-brains-412485.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她其後改變主意，與Storm Models簽約，其下所屬還有超級名模[[凱特·摩斯|凱特·摩斯]]（Kate Moss）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://onethousandmodels.com/lilycole/lilycole.html |title=Lily Cole Photos, Pictures, Galleries, Forum, Bio, Stats & Tags - Lily Cole - One Thousand Models : Runway, Glamour, Swimsuit, and Supermodels |publisher=One Thousand Models |date= |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2009-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090222201518/http://onethousandmodels.com/lilycole/lilycole.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

她擁有一頭紅髮，是少數能夠成為名模的紅髮模特兒。她被歸屬於有精靈和娃娃臉特徵的模特兒<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/education/education-news/from-catwalk-to-cambridge-lily-cole-to-study-for-degree-410876.html |title=From catwalk to Cambridge: Lily Cole to study for degree |publisher=The Independent |date=2006-08-07 |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2009-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090116162028/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/education/education-news/from-catwalk-to-cambridge-lily-cole-to-study-for-degree-410876.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，就像[[希瑟·馬克斯|希瑟·馬克斯]]、[[吉瑪·沃德|吉瑪·沃德]]和[[戴文·青木|戴文·青木]]般。

她是[[馬莎百貨|馬莎百貨]]服裝廣告的模特兒，亦是服裝廣告系列中最年輕的模特兒。莉莉成為馬莎限量服裝系列中唯一的面孔<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fashionunited.co.uk/News/Columns/Lily_Cole_new_face_of_M&S_200711172314/ |title=Lily Cole new face of M&S - Fashion news, jobs, fashion career, directory, job board FashionUnited, network, design, London, UK |publisher=Fashionunited.co.uk |date=2007-11-17 |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2009-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208003153/http://www.fashionunited.co.uk/News/Columns/Lily_Cole_new_face_of_M%26S_200711172314/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2007年，莉莉被提名為英國時尚大獎（British Fashion Awards）「年度模特兒」（Model of the Year），但大獎最終歸入[[艾潔妮絲·迪恩|艾潔妮絲·迪恩]]（Agyness Deyn）手中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/daily/2007-11/071127-british-fashion-award-winners-2007.aspx |title=British Fashion Awards 2007 - check out who won what (Vogue.com UK) |publisher=Vogue.co.uk |date=2007-11-27 |accessdate=2009-02-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090718013311/http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/daily/2007-11/071127-british-fashion-award-winners-2007.aspx |archivedate=2009-07-18 }}</ref>。

2008年，《[[星期日泰晤士報|星期日泰晤士報]]》估計莉莉共賺得6百萬英鎊<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1029278/Lily-Cole-handsome-new-companion-lead-glamour-pack-star-studded-gala.html |title=Lily Cole and her handsome new companion lead the glamour pack at star-studded gala | Mail Online |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date=2008-06-25 |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2008-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207080744/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1029278/Lily-Cole-handsome-new-companion-lead-glamour-pack-star-studded-gala.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她在英國獲排名最富有年青人第77位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://business.timesonline.co.uk/tol/business/specials/rich_list/article3799140.ece |title=Lily Cole |publisher=The Sunday Times |date=2008-04-27 |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2009-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090502175824/http://business.timesonline.co.uk/tol/business/specials/rich_list/article3799140.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

同年10月，莉莉全裸登在《[[花花公子|花花公子]]》的封面及內頁中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.marieclaire.co.uk/news/fashion/275919/see-lily-cole-pose-for-playboy.html |title=See Lily Cole pose for Playboy |publisher=Marie Claire |date=2008-10-02 |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2009-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090212131136/http://www.marieclaire.co.uk/news/fashion/275919/see-lily-cole-pose-for-playboy.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/celebritynews/2967379/Marks-and-Spencer-model-Lily-Cole-to-bare-all-in-French-Playboy.html |title=Marks and Spencer model Lily Cole to bare all in French Playboy |publisher=Daily Telegraph |date=2008-09-16 |accessdate=2009-03-20 |archive-date=2009-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090212140957/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/celebritynews/2967379/Marks-and-Spencer-model-Lily-Cole-to-bare-all-in-French-Playboy.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她在照片中拿著一隻小熊，身上沒有穿任何衣服，除了一雙白襪<ref>{{cite web |url=http://timworstall.typepad.com/timworstall/2008/10/lily-cole-in-pl.html |title=Lily Cole in Playboy |publisher=Timworstall.typepad.com |date= |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2009-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104050752/http://timworstall.typepad.com/timworstall/2008/10/lily-cole-in-pl.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這輯照片被受爭議，有人甚至要求馬莎百貨中斷與莉莉的合約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Marks-And-Spencer-Model-Lily-Cole-Poses-For-Playboy-Cover/Article/200810115112713 |title=Marks And Spencer Model Lily Cole Poses For Playboy Cover |publisher=Sly News |date= |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2009-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090223114351/http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Marks-And-Spencer-Model-Lily-Cole-Poses-For-Playboy-Cover/Article/200810115112713 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sponkit.com/lily-cole-thinks-her-french-playboy-photo-is-art/ |title=Lily Cole Thinks Her French Playboy Photo Is Art |publisher=Sponkit.com |date= |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2008-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202135402/http://www.sponkit.com/lily-cole-thinks-her-french-playboy-photo-is-art/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。馬莎百貨聲明他們會繼續使用莉莉，認為莉莉「是個有名氣，形象高而且需求量大的模特兒，這是我們安排她為我們工作的其中一個主要原因。」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/daily/081006-ms-defends-lily-cole-for-playboy.aspx?DisplayComments=true |title=M&S defends Lily Cole's Playboy shoot |publisher=Vogue.co.uk |date=2008-10-06 |accessdate=2009-02-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208235231/http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/daily/081006-ms-defends-lily-cole-for-playboy.aspx?DisplayComments=true |archivedate=2008-12-08 }}</ref>。該品牌的發言人強調，「這全然是自己的選擇去接受其他的工作，我們並不希望妨礙她的工作事業。」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.echo-news.co.uk/uk_national_entertainment/3727227.M_S_model_makes_Playboy_debut/ |title=M&S model makes Playboy debut |publisher=Echo-news.co.uk |date=2008-10-03 |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2008-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081224093725/http://www.echo-news.co.uk/uk_national_entertainment/3727227.M_S_model_makes_Playboy_debut/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。莉莉也被《Paradis》雜誌拍攝全裸照<ref>{{cite web |url=http://fashioncopious.typepad.com/fashioncopious/2007/12/lily-cole-bares.html |title=Lily Cole Bares all for Paradis & Teller |publisher=Fashioncopious.typepad.com |date=2007-12-10 |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071217124242/http://fashioncopious.typepad.com/fashioncopious/2007/12/lily-cole-bares.html |archivedate=2007-12-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>
。

